des:
Barence products help you control home appliance.You can simply ask Alexa to turn on or turn off your switch.
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust your switch - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo.
After connecting Alexa to your Barence products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "Barence" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register an account in our "Barence" app;
(3). You need to have some Barence devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "Barence" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Barence Smart" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Barence Smart" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Barence Smart", and you'll be navigated to "Barence Smart" login page;
(9). Input your Barence account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the switch.”
“Alexa, turn off the switch.”
